  "logNo": "220896240084",
  "title": "이수한의원의 크리스마스는 언제나 늘 그랬듯이 이번 2016년에도 따뜻하다",
  "addDate": "2016. 12. 27.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220896240084",
  "html_size": 194590,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220896240084\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220896240084\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">토요일은 일주일 중에 최고 바쁜 요일이다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이번 12월 24일 토요일은</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">크리스마스 이브날이었다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">주 1~2회 이수한의원에 오시는 환자분께서 치료를 받고 가셨는데</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">조금있다 다시 오셨다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">뭘 두고 가신 줄 알았는데</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">양손에 이걸 가지고 오셨다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/05c22bd31284d736.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjdfMTgy/MDAxNDgyODI5NTY3NDU5.Dnq-eOg1dvqyuPbpSbfbzW0R065IfMHVqE8WcL6Whcgg.GifSFA8tEos7KHQQNls9f8AReD3jNYhq51Sz3znBfKQg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161227_170942820.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E7121D4')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/05c22bd31284d736.jpg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">일때문에 바빠서 열어볼 시간은 없고</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">퇴근하고 집으로 가져왔다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이수한의원 선생님들이 총 4명이라고 일부러 4개 사오셨다고 하셨다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">감사합니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">#꾸벅</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">하나만 사오셔도 감사한데</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">짱이십니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">ㅎㅎㅎ</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c55fd9d746e00f68.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-44\"></a>&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">궁굼해서</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">집에 가자마자 케잌을 열어봤는데</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">짠~</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e3b6be5366f1ac7f.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjdfMTUg/MDAxNDgyODI5NTY3NzEw.EcVAWcsI3RQ3g4Ae_dAvoyp8FBwVJY7eQ80B9uHq7ksg.GAgwCFjX1ttBGWJqNX7pfyKmYqHjpjuzsc_eDtH56mEg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161227_170942987.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E7121D4')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e3b6be5366f1ac7f.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">너무 이쁘고 귀엽다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c2960e237ec66fff.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjdfMTIz/MDAxNDgyODI5NTY3ODgz.50Q3zUcdgkUzqFDvTKjoL-NEDdTmdu7ZBPqSFNVPZe8g.9T9KWlFnAyTBqDXumceJ7KISPLXESssUKmbT_k8RI_Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161227_170943124.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E7121D4')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c2960e237ec66fff.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">위에서 찍는다고 찍었는데</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">뭔가 이상하다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">.</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">.</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">.</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">.</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">.</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">.</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">.</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">.</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">.</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">찾으셨나요??</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><div align=\"center\"><div align=\"center\">다 부러져있었다</div><div align=\"center\">내가 들고가다 부러진건가?</div><div align=\"center\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\">ㅠㅠ</div><div>&nbsp;</div></div></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d574ec9ad492f86b.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjdfMjEw/MDAxNDgyODI5NTY4MDU0.WRVU-l2-IKcWIsDKpvNKQ_lCey3LzT1HKKghdOYtfQkg.WDrLnUKnNIDayTHJCed6Gg0sBf3wsBaHSsfOSi4lELMg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161227_170943287.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E7121D4')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d574ec9ad492f86b.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><div align=\"center\">그래서 손으로 잡고 다시 찍었다</div><div align=\"center\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/64e9b72df78c6cf4.png\" style=\"border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" alt=\"moon_and_james-35\"></a></div><div align=\"center\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/349282194b75bfce.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjdfMjUy/MDAxNDgyODI5NTY4NzI4.9rF7OZGhgsq7B5NLAYkVwocjDtzjyIlAdVVmbTJG2fsg.OObde8aaJCoTl-W3frTyWeYuIDV953m1WwhsfDW2clAg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161227_170943575.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E7121D4')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/349282194b75bfce.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">감쪽같다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/29c736df8f29e67e.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjdfMiAg/MDAxNDgyODI5NTY4MjUx.tSH6apCk5jQiY4-6nxko_Q96YUKmTemKNRr5Kk_KmFcg.qUg5NnE6jYUVYDZ1i7gNG3Pyh8EfPM-mOqD5eXw0jc4g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161227_170943439.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E7121D4')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/29c736df8f29e67e.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">불쌍한 루돌프</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">다시 붙여서 잡고 찍어줬는데</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">다 찍고 머리통은 내입속으로 쓩</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b9243b143cddae20.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-25\"></a>&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">암튼...</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7e172990e8317681.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMjdfOTYg/MDAxNDgyODI5NTY4OTEz.CN3HgviAQ1HC2w3efSq992-i7jWtUT7JooQksPq8wbcg.D57E1SMrw3391XhwrRsfN_XIqdoXqiswP6vV8ENzhHUg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161227_170943716.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336E7121D4')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7e172990e8317681.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">메리크리스마스~</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">케잌 주신 우리 이수한의원 환자분께 다시 한번 감사의 마음을 전하고싶습니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">감사합니다^^</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">행복하세요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
